urdu transliteration text:
ALAM JO KAHLI HUSSEIN LAYEHARAM YEH SAMJEH ABBAS AIYE HAR EK BASHA ALAM SE RO KARLIPAT GAYYA HAIN
The children thought Abbas had come,
@HujjatELC

RABAAB CHEEKI KOIEE TO AIYEUTHA KE BIMAR KO JO LAYE KOIEE LUTHERA HAMARE KHAMEIN JHALLA RAHA HAIN
Rubab shouted, Someone please come
@HujjatELC

NA DAIR MAQTAL MAIN AB LAGAWOCHALLA KEIN GALLDI ASSIR LAWO LAIYEEN ABID KO TAIZEYANE LAGA RAHA HAI
Walk quickly and bring the captives,
@HujjatELC
